---
import Section from "@components/Section.astro";
import { Signal, MapPin, Database } from "lucide-astro";
---

<Section title="The Mission" id="mission">
  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
    <div>
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Code with a Conscience</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-400 mb-6 text-lg">
        We aren't looking for the next crypto-exchange. We are looking for
        "Quiet Giants"â€”boring, critical software that solves logistical and
        survival problems in low-resource environments.
      </p>
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div
          class="flex gap-4 p-4 rounded-lg bg-gray-900 border border-gray-800 hover:border-yellow-500/50 transition-colors"
        >
          <Signal class="text-yellow-500 shrink-0 mt-1" />
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-bold text-white">mPedigree Style Verification</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">
              Counterfeit malaria drugs kill thousands. Systems that use simple
              SMS codes on flip phones to verify medicine authenticity save
              lives.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div
          class="flex gap-4 p-4 rounded-lg bg-gray-900 border border-gray-800 hover:border-yellow-500/50 transition-colors"
        >
          <MapPin class="text-yellow-500 shrink-0 mt-1" />
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-bold text-white">Ushahidi Crisis Mapping</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">
              Crowdsourcing reports during disasters. When the power goes out,
              how do communities organize aid?
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div
          class="flex gap-4 p-4 rounded-lg bg-gray-900 border border-gray-800 hover:border-yellow-500/50 transition-colors"
        >
          <Database class="text-yellow-500 shrink-0 mt-1" />
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-bold text-white">CommCare / DHIS2</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">
              Offline-first medical records. Helping rural health workers track
              patient history in areas with zero internet.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div
      class="bg-gray-900 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-gray-800 relative overflow-hidden group hover:border-yellow-500/30 transition-all"
    >
      <div
        class="absolute top-0 right-0 p-4 opacity-10 group-hover:opacity-20 transition-opacity"
      >
        <Signal size={120} />
      </div>
      <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-yellow-500 mb-4">Prompt Inspiration</h4>
      <div
        class="bg-black p-4 rounded font-mono text-sm text-green-400 border border-gray-800 mb-4"
      >
        <span class="text-gray-500">// Example Prompt</span><br />
        "Build an SMS-based inventory bot for rural pharmacies that runs on 2G
        networks..."
      </div>
      <div
        class="bg-black p-4 rounded font-mono text-sm text-green-400 border border-gray-800"
      >
        <span class="text-gray-500">// Example Prompt</span><br />
        "Create a peer-to-peer mesh network app for locating fresh water sources
        during a flood..."
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Section>
